This paper is about mitigating gender bias in word embeddings, which is a topic related to natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a method that utilizes statistical dependency, which suggests that it may fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the evaluation of the proposed method, which may fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
